title: Wide Receiver sleepers and busts
itunes:title: Wide Receiver sleepers and busts
description:
A room filled with heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler – give you their second installment of the fantasy extravaganza by running through all of the wide outs that could help or hurt your team this season. The guys also take you behind the scenes in Cleveland and the Mike Pettine regime following Sessler's long form, Believeland.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
